{"tid":386791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聖書院40歲吳姓男教師 涉性侵至少5女學生","createTime":"2017-09-04T07:13:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T05:32:40.000Z","uid":92301,"like":30,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"87fb4a3a79c97a5637584af99aa678519a96fdfb","tid":386791,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:13:21.000Z","msg":"有中聖書院學生揭發，一名身兼基督教團體身份的40歲男教師，過去3年涉持續性騷擾最少兩名女生，多次於私家車上涉非禮女學生。該男教師連環物色受害者身邊人，兩女學生估計連同自己共有5名受害女學生，事件今年6月在校內首曝光，男教師隨即離職並銷聲匿迹，警方及教育局已介入調查。<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌性騷擾及性侵犯女學生的姓吳教師現年40歲，已婚並育有一女，於深水埗中聖書院任教最少15年，校內深受學生愛戴。他在校內及多個基督教團體擔任多項要職。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，吳本身不時以私家車載女學生出入，校內多名教師亦對他的行為有微言，但因吳向來對學生熱情親切，認為只是寵愛學生。現年18歲的女學生X及17歲的女學生Y指，吳過往3年常以其私家車分別載她們出入校園，並於晚上私下載到寂靜位置，在車上性侵。<br />\n<br />\nX指2014年接近暑假時，吳有次載她到青馬大橋觀景台正式表白，X拒絕並感到被非禮，認為該次是人生污點。開學後吳常纏擾X及多次觸摸其手及面，「佢好煩，不停求你見佢，如果我見佢十幾分鐘可以令佢收聲一陣，咁我見囉」，情況持續一年。<br />\n<br />\n或另有3人受害<br />\n<br />\n至2015年吳結識X的好友Y，轉移目標到Y身上，同樣接載Y上學及放學，並於2016年向Y示愛，指當Y是女兒般疼愛，並非男女關係。Y指吳其後常於晚上7時後，載她到學校附近寂靜位置，於私家車上對她強吻及摸胸、捉着她手摸自己下體、要求看Y底褲等，「當初我喺佢架車上面覺得唔舒服，想開車門走時，佢即刻鎖門，之後每次我都覺我唔會走得甩，而且佢會講我唔見佢，佢要食藥，情感上我好驚，覺得唔可以走」。<br />\n<br />\n直至今年暑假前，Y發現吳轉移目標到其好友身上，她估計校內最少有5名女學生疑被性騷擾。二人向學校投訴，學校即設危機小組並進行調查及報警，7月中，校方向全校教職員出通告，指吳已辭職。二人因擔心吳會到新學校任教，並有其他學生受害，故公開披露事件。<br />\n<br />\n中聖書院校長曹美娟不回應吳是被辭退還是自行辭職。她指校方收到投訴後啟動危機小組，警方接手調查後，校方已停止調查。有知情人士批評，校方報警後不再繼續調查是不當，指吳離職不代表解決事件。而大部份教師亦不知吳被投訴。<br />\n<br />\n協助兩名學生的立法會議員鄺俊宇要求校方嚴肅處理，指危機小組應繼續調查，擔心該教師會在其他學校繼續性侵犯學生。警方回覆，兩名女子指被一名男子非禮，兩宗案件合併交由葵青警區刑事調查隊第三隊跟進。並於7月18日在沙田區以涉嫌非禮拘捕一名40歲男子。該名男子獲准保釋，9月中向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170904/20142148\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170904%2F20142148&d=ZHrH1%2FwvHXf6jfny9QUxD4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=25441155\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170904%2F20142148&h=b60917ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170904/20142148</a><br />\n教畜仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79ce830edceade05b708f829f45b183ef280d98d","tid":386791,"uid":122115,"like":56,"dislike":2,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:17:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">他在校內及多個基督教團體擔任多項要職。</span><br />\n<br />\n信教果啲個腦真係痴痴地線"},{"pid":"7662739f1b267de6720a7b2d8f7103e17dff6cc0","tid":386791,"uid":50801,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">他在校內及多個基督教團體擔任多項要職。</span><br />\n<br />\n信教果啲個腦真係痴痴地線</blockquote><br />\n信教都有性需要，上帝俾既考驗(不過過唔到)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adda37d236a7103b6f9c4ca73fb5a89cee6db785","tid":386791,"uid":79353,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">他在校內及多個基督教團體擔任多項要職。</span><br />\n<br />\n信教果啲個腦真係痴痴地線</blockquote><br />\n信教都有性需要，上帝俾既考驗(不過過唔到)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n不過過唔到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ab0c645ada783cba2f36d742e40f456c613133","tid":386791,"uid":67237,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:31:29.000Z","msg":"d耶撚真係好撚虛偽<br />\n屋企都有件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a025af26fd18e227ae3fe1b2151f1a58a86d9423","tid":386791,"uid":26952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"X同Y係兩姊妹,識食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"687de592040ad520cd8655a9bd1172e3433c0258","tid":386791,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c59623af47081d57c1bc4dbefae2360ef0b7097","tid":386791,"uid":102700,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:33:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/153259_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F153259_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png&h=df6dbc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nthats why"},{"pid":"f2f281203fed676ecc245bc4b89ea2733fecb227","tid":386791,"uid":11148,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:34:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/153259_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F153259_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png&h=df6dbc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nthats why</blockquote><br />\n40歲 ? 60歲差唔兔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757bc6d99e7aebb8ac1d6ab896e234719b600994","tid":386791,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:34:53.000Z","msg":"博恩浸信會有限公司董事，但今年1月已辭去董事一職。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"523f9d98c91bea5b9f1ac3e95d50b18549250992","tid":386791,"uid":11148,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:35:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/153259_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F153259_a19ddbe22afc139c538bfca41cea40ad.png&h=df6dbc74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nthats why</blockquote><br />\n40歲 ? 60歲差唔<span style=\"color: red;\">多</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"95822dec654fc55d1b001a0bc44eba71e2b184dd","tid":386791,"uid":26952,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:38:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/153808_465bb7601a4d527d102afdf737d64809.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F153808_465bb7601a4d527d102afdf737d64809.jpg&h=913dacec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4dd367d7de9de3e42bbef250885d974e6099290f","tid":386791,"uid":810,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:40:31.000Z","msg":"做教畜真係正 <br />\n又食又拎"},{"pid":"cdf37f144bbbf42bc0baa0f34845590402a23892","tid":386791,"uid":997,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:46:37.000Z","msg":"深水埗中聖書院爆出懷疑男教師非禮女學生事件，受害兩名女生分別為17及18歲，其中一人遭非禮逾一年半，行為包括濕吻、摸大腿及胸、被捉手強行觸摸男方下體，兩女啞忍多時，今年6月終向校方投訴並報警。據了解，該男教師已被警方以涉嫌非禮拘捕，獲准保釋候查。該校今日(4日)在學校網頁刊登新聞稿，指有關教師已於7月中辭職，事件交由警方調查。<br />\n<br />\n該學校網頁表示，該校於6月底接獲學生就相關教師涉嫌有不恰當行為之投訴，已隨即請輔導主任及社工了解事件，並為學生進行情緒支援，與學生家長交代事件，又暫停有關教師的職務。學生由社工及教師陪同下報警，該校已將事件向教育局通報。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，涉事的吳姓男教師在該校任教超過10年，更擔任校內基督教小組主任，已婚並育有一女。<span style=\"color: red;\">有消息指，他得悉事件曝光後，主動向學校辭職，並已在一間特殊學校覓得教席</span>。負責協助兩位受害女生的立法會議員鄺俊宇表示，吳一得知學校展開調查，即主動離職，令學校調查被迫中止，避過受責及暫停教席。<br />\n<br />\n鄺指出，吳涉嫌經常以關愛學生為由接載放學，並載到僻靜處施以獸行。東網正向教育局及警方查詢，未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170904/bkn-20170904105016810-0904_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170904%2Fbkn-20170904105016810-0904_00822_001.html&d=ZHrH1%2FwvHXf6jfny9QUxD4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=46581931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170904/bkn-20170904105016810-0904_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲識得避去特殊學校搵食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0279058e6f6f96cc34f81831704da296bb983c01","tid":386791,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:52:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做教畜真係正 <br />\n又食又拎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCLS, 破晒囡囡處"},{"pid":"3fa169864541f4c953487e0b1ec59f88d874dd59","tid":386791,"uid":1874,"like":4,"dislike":6,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做教畜真係正 <br />\n又食又拎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nCLS, 破晒囡囡處</blockquote><br />\nBand3 MK中學黎，邊度仲有處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4d7ceb69e0612891210650c7a118e93472ae536","tid":386791,"uid":28838,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:11:23.000Z","msg":"耶撚表示：係神指引我老強你"},{"pid":"95ec3a7ade9547efeae803c9d9ac1d41fc28fda1","tid":386791,"uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:21:23.000Z","msg":"俾人非禮成年唔出聲？？？<br />\n<br />\n有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4406106da6f7f688a40997ffe9471a6061ad0f3b","tid":386791,"uid":4285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:23:35.000Z","msg":"叫雞啦，　仆街"},{"pid":"ee5756487c445d6951ddb650c7c30bc8758dc0b6","tid":386791,"uid":19919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:31:38.000Z","msg":"香港+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5b59fae742dacae8297c03f16e57f7f944beb2","tid":386791,"uid":5476